export interface LanguageCode {
  code: string;
  value: string;
}

export const convertLanguageCodes = (codes: string[]) => {
  return codes.map(l => ({
    code: l,

    // NOTE(SHAHAN): We want to backup to the language code in case
    // we do not have the name conversion. The languages can change over time.
    value: RFCLanguageTags[l] || l,
  }));
};
